structure.unit: B LICENSURE AND REGULATION OF HEALTH FACILITIES AND SERVICES

law.catch_line: KRS 216B.300 to 216B.320 not applicable to boarding home regulated by federal government.
law.text: The provisions of KRS 216B.300 to 216B.320 shall not apply to any boarding home operated or regulated by the federal government.
law.history: Created 1990 Ky. Acts ch. 439, sec. 5, effective July 13, 1990.
